  • Package org.example.eiscuno.model.card.cardEffect

    • Class org.example.eiscuno.model.card.cardEffect.CardEffect

      class CardEffect extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • cardEffect
          ICardEffect cardEffect
          The specific effect behavior associated with a card.

          This can be one of several implementations:

          • DrawTwoEffect
          • DrawFourEffect
          • ColorEffect
          • SkipEffect
          If no effect is set, this attribute may remain null, meaning the card is a normal number card with no special effect.
